/*+ NoHashJoin(cc cct2 cct1) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 t mi_idx) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 mi_idx t it2) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 it2 mi_idx t mk) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 it2 mi_idx mk t k) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 it2 k mi_idx mk t kt) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 it2 k kt mi mi_idx mk t mc) NoNestLoop(cc cct1 cct2 it2 k kt mc mi mi_idx mk t ct) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ct it2 k kt mc mi mi_idx mk t cn) NoNestLoop(cc cct1 cct2 cn ct it2 k kt mc mi mi_idx mk t it1) */ select min(cn.name) AS movie_company,
min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS complete_euro_dark_movie
from complete_cast AS cc
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind <> 'complete+verified'
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind = 'crew'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2000
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8.5'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'murder-in-title',
'blood',
'violence')
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie',
'episode')
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Denmark',
'Swedish',
'Norwegian',
'Bulgaria',
'Sweden',
'America',
'English',
'Denish',
'Norway',
'Danish')
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.note not like '%(USA)%' AND mc.note like '%(200%)%'
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code <> '[us]'
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries';
